      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "この日のために新しい衣装を作って……\n内緒で会場を準備して……",
      "startTime": 18.7999997138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "あの時伝えられなかった感謝の気持ちを……",
      "startTime": 21.2999997138,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
