      "text": "（……麻奈ちゃん。あなたの想いが詰まった曲を）\n（あなたの後輩達が心を込めて歌うわ）",
      "startTime": 158.7666769344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈……君は歌でみんなを笑顔にするのが好きだったな）\n（その心は、今も後輩達の中で息づいているぞ）",
      "startTime": 168.2333344458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wing"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "（これは星見プロの過去と未来をつなぐ歌……）",
      "startTime": 173.3000011125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_08_03-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "（歌に込められた私達の気持ち）\n（みんなに伝わるって信じてるから！）",
      "startTime": 179.9999980607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
